{"tid":511692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾虛報遊泰時遭輪姦而入獄 港女承認上月於街頭偷手機","createTime":"2017-12-27T17:22:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-27T22:54:58.000Z","uid":13468,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fc9fc4eab43dace6f4ee1b76b38c52d52cc8abf8","tid":511692,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"曾虛報遊泰時遭輪姦而入獄 港女承認上月於街頭偷手機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多年前曾於泰國曼谷虛報遭輪姦而入獄的女子蘇亮熒，上月於旺角街頭扒竊男途人手機遭巡警人贓並獲。蘇繼而向警員出示他人的身份證副本以圖掩飾身分。她今在裁判法院承認盜竊及明知地誤導警員罪，辯稱因經濟壓力犯案，惟裁判官認為她是因毒癮所致。<br />\n<br />\n蘇亮熒（43歲）過往共有7個案底，由於部份跟毒品有關，裁判官認為被告犯案是因毒癮所致，故為被告索取戒毒所報告，押至明年1月10日判刑。<br />\n據控方案情指，今年11月26日下午6時警員在旺角西洋菜街附近發現被告行為可疑，及後見她從男途人的右後褲袋偷走一部iPhone 6手機然後逃走。警員上前截查，被告承認手機屬於男途人，她並自稱「李彩平」，指自己遺失了身份證，只向警員出示「李彩平」身份證副本及入境處預約紙。警誡下，被告稱打算變賣手機。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171227/57632223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57632223&d=e063JNSVJALsVg7jAJDt7dr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=cc103a18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171227%2F57632223&h=31ebb213\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171227/57632223</a>"},{"pid":"5acbf4f8417554b01ec6ec4be9f8a4d443eb9543","tid":511692,"uid":7840,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T17:25:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5d0210518ef57de2439ac9454e2d63b026b66b40","tid":511692,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T17:27:41.000Z","msg":"6都偷"},{"pid":"2d6fb63131a8571249d688972b31a237ee4ac970","tid":511692,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T20:50:04.000Z","msg":"好人好姐系列"},{"pid":"21358e5015468b71c18b98ad6d59f59235546fa8","tid":511692,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T21:13:44.000Z","msg":"如果當時個男途人想攞返部電話實比佢me too<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098300636067d4f71cb88b6dd91e3de9f9a9aedc","tid":511692,"uid":62011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T22:12:30.000Z","msg":"mark 呢單野先，d人成日話一個女仔好人好者做咩屈人強奸，宜家有證據啦。原來港女好人好者真係會屈人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7258d4a9c14814f319f88fcd02ddcad70acae29","tid":511692,"uid":23021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T22:13:19.000Z","msg":"抵"},{"pid":"e57febb386813ae291fc1564bbbb140dc2fc4396","tid":511692,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T22:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebed4c905d731adc258302122008d73049a3c13e","tid":511692,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-27T22:54:58.000Z","msg":"港女有被害妄想<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}